citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba93e87afcd1f041ad9f0fd65484bac60fd50cc","tid":1506272,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:07:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-free-6090078-1.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbs.tianya.cn%2Fm%2Fpost-free-6090078-1.shtml&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=36458de3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-free-6090078-1.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n以前流行一句說話<br />\n<br />\n南高登 北天涯<br />\n<br />\n天涯討論區算是在極權之下<br />\n<br />\n稍為有開放思想的中國討論區<br />\n<br />\n其中有網民說<br />\n<br />\n【呵呵，谁敢说现在的香港不会成为秦朝的大泽乡？】<br />\n<br />\n反秦起義就是大澤鄉 陳勝吳廣起義<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n網民Ａ<br />\n<br />\n工作一辈子，都买不起房子，看不到想希望，你觉得，要咋整？<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｂ<br />\n<br />\n从娃娃抓起，爱国？无私奉献？抬高房价？年轻人生存都成了问题，还教育什么？<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｃ<br />\n<br />\n社会制度不同，就像水和火一样不可调和。除非水变火，火变水。<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｄ<br />\n<br />\n说好了是50年不变，为什么20多年就想变、就想改、就像当家做主，这也太急了。<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｅ<br />\n<br />\n你要爬在地上，什么 ，还想站着，你的思想觉悟呢，你的家国情怀呢<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｆ<br />\n<br />\n非慕洋犬们为什么会在瑞士银行有7.8万亿，这也是匪夷所思的事情<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｇ<br />\n<br />\n现在网络这么发达，监控头这么多，为什么电视报道、现场直播等视频都没有？到底是怎样的暴徒，能否像报道法国黄背心一样报道<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n不能盡錄 香港人要加油<br />\n<br />\n牆內很多人也默默支持香港示威者"},{"pid":"91e446f97b683306282c08046af39d0d156f438e","tid":1506272,"uid":67252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd7bdf5246f1954d68652ff6ca8a1710cde435f","tid":1506272,"uid":259613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bQfgi0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bQfgi0.jpg&h=b52f8b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yARBLcm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyARBLcm.png&h=f8e33375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rdA67qH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrdA67qH.jpg&h=6c639eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acfd3a142cf3980d812503de212f421efd05a756","tid":1506272,"uid":67252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6745eef6783447faca20b2a689f0468ed7ad02d1","tid":1506272,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:09:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dfa10a8876cd19c966470617af800dafd3010133","tid":1506272,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:09:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c65adc1a7f40ed6f89d31964135e8f14da16ba36","tid":1506272,"uid":270739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:09:27.000Z","msg":"無恥到核爆"},{"pid":"d125d060f57a5caf8402b0ac4e0184c627937ff1","tid":1506272,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:09:49.000Z","msg":"錫之前記得話電光火石之間冇時間做判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398b2dc3bb9e3f94074169b9e586a9a51d719dcd","tid":1506272,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:09:58.000Z","msg":"哇自然反應？見住一個人跪喺度自然反應竟然係去踢佢<br />\n同你見到曱甴打死佢有咩分別"},{"pid":"137937b2a62479018356f7079fe1b471f68e6b0e","tid":1506272,"uid":29942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:10:20.000Z","msg":"普通市民自然反應黑警，一早比狗拉左啦"},{"pid":"75cb0edc3291a4db855522c99f81f16cee257ff9","tid":1506272,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:10:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開學日大家醒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"h